data.description: Large one level true ranch and situated on 2+/- acres in Hall County. Just a short drive to Dawsonville, Dahlongea, and Gainesville. No HOA and no restrictions so bring your chickens, horse, or any other livestock your heart desires. Just under 3 miles to Kroger, CVS, and lots of other retail. This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths with one half bath. All bedrooms and hallway have fresh paint along with new waterproof LVP flooring. The living room has new waterproof LVP and an accent wall added with hand stained wood to give you that warm feeling with a side of life. The kitchen is all brand new and features a true farmhouse style sink along with new stainless appliances. Kitchen also has new waterproof LVP installed. There is also an oversized 2 car garage along with a one vehicle car port.  Brand new 15 seer 4 ton Lennox A/C and new high efficiency 2 stage gas furnace.. new duct work with complete UV protection and electronic filtration. Property also features what appears to be an old building that may have been used as a machine shop years ago, but currently being used as storage. There is also another storage building to the rear of the house. If you are looking for your slice of heaven in Hall County that is just a hop to Lake Lanier, this is the ONE.
